    • extractPeopleInfo

      public static String[] extractPeopleInfo(Statement statement, String query) throws SQLException
      Extract the architect name, contractor name, and customer name that are related to a specific project.
      Parameters:
      statement - A Direct Line to the database for running our queries.
      query - A SQL query that filters one specific row in the PROJECTS table, and shows it to us.
      Returns:
      Return a String Array that contains the architect name, contractor name, customer first name, and customer last name.
      Throws:
      SQLException

    • captureProject

      public static String[] captureProject()
      A function that encapsulates a total of 13 different unit functions. The unit functions are as follows: (1) capturePrjName, (2) capturePrjDueDte, (3) capturePmName, (4) captureArchtName, (5) captureContrName, (6) captureCustFname, (7) captureCustLname, (8) captureStructEngName, (9) captureBldgType, (10) capturePhysAddr, (11) CaptureErfNo, (12) captureTotalFee, (13) captureTotalPtd.
      Returns:
      A string array of 13 values gets returned back to the calling function. These values are then used to construct a new project in the PoisePMS Database.

    • captureArchitect

      public static String[] captureArchitect()
      A function that encapsulates 4 other unit functions, which are as follows: (1) captureArchtName, (2) captureArchtTelNo, (3) captureArchtEmail, (4) captureArchtPhysAddr.
      Returns:
      Return a string array of 4 values back to the calling functions. These values are then used to construct a new Architect entity in the ARCHITECTS table.

    • captureCustomer

      public static String[] captureCustomer()
      A function that encapsulates 5 other unit functions, which are as follows: (1) captureCustFname, (2) captureCustLname, (3) captureCustTelno, (4) captureCustEmail, (5) captureCustPhysAddr.
      Returns:
      Return an array of five String values back to the calling function. These values are then used to construct a new Customer Entity in the CUSTOMERS table.

    • captureContractor

      public static String[] captureContractor()
